    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT MNC Digital Entertainment Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, engages in producing, developing, and distributing content and intellectual properties across various media platforms in Indonesia. It operates through Content, IP & Others; Online Advertising; and Subscription segments. The company is involved in media and entertainment activities, such as drama production houses, infotainment, reality shows, game shows, animation, films, original content, micro drama, and music labels. It also acts as an advertising and talent agency; provides content and IP licensing; and operates social media, including multi-channel networks (MCN) and digital marketing, as well as OTT superapps, RCTI+ (AVOD Superapp) & Vision+ (SVOD Superapp). The company was formerly known as PT MNC Studios International TBK and changed its name to PT MNC Digital Entertainment Tbk in March 2022. PT MNC Digital Entertainment Tbk was founded in 2000 and is based in Jakarta Barat, Indonesia. The company operates as a subsidiary of PT Media Nusantara Citra Tbk.",
